### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@adminToken = your-admin-token-here
@comptableToken = your-comptable-token-here
@clientToken = your-client-token-here

# documentCategory must be a Document.TypeDocument value:
#   FACTURE_ACHAT | FACTURE_VENTE | TICKET_CAISSE | RELEVE_BANCAIRE

### ==================== CREATE (ADMIN + COMPTABLE) ====================

### Create Deadline - FACTURE_ACHAT (status auto-computed from dueDate)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Create Deadline - RELEVE_BANCAIRE (explicit UPCOMING)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-09-30",
  "documentCategory": "RELEVE_BANCAIRE",
  "status": "UPCOMING"
}

### Create Deadline - FACTURE_VENTE (past dueDate → auto OVERDUE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 2,
  "fiscalYear": 2023,
  "dueDate": "2024-03-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_VENTE"
}

### Create Deadline - TICKET_CAISSE (explicitly COMPLETED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2023,
  "dueDate": "2024-06-30",
  "documentCategory": "TICKET_CAISSE",
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### ==================== READ (ADMIN + COMPTABLE + CLIENT) ====================

### Get All Deadlines (default: page=0, size=10, sortBy=dueDate, sortDir=asc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Custom Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?page=0&size=5&sortBy=dueDate&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Filter by societe (CLIENT scopes to their own societeId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?societeId=1&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Filter by status UPCOMING
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?status=UPCOMING&page=0&size=10&sortBy=dueDate&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Filter by status OVERDUE
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?status=OVERDUE&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Filter by status COMPLETED
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?status=COMPLETED&page=0&size=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Get All Deadlines - Combine societe + status filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines?societeId=1&status=UPCOMING&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Deadline By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### ==================== UPDATE (ADMIN + COMPTABLE) ====================

### Full Update - change dueDate and documentCategory
PUT {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-10-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Full Update - mark as COMPLETED via full update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-09-30",
  "documentCategory": "RELEVE_BANCAIRE",
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Patch Status - mark COMPLETED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1/status?status=COMPLETED
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Patch Status - mark OVERDUE manually
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/2/status?status=OVERDUE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Patch Status - reopen as UPCOMING
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/3/status?status=UPCOMING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==================== DELETE (ADMIN + COMPTABLE) ====================

### Delete Deadline - admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete Deadline - comptable
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/2
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### ==================== OVERDUE REFRESH (ADMIN + COMPTABLE) ====================

### Refresh Overdue Statuses - bulk-marks past-due deadlines as OVERDUE
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/refresh-overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Refresh Overdue Statuses - with comptable token
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/refresh-overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### ==================== ERROR CASES ====================

### Create - Missing required field societeId (should fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Create - Missing documentCategory (should fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31"
}

### Create - Invalid documentCategory value (should fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "TVA"
}

### Create - fiscalYear out of range (should fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 1999,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Create - Non-existent societeId (should fail - 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 9999,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Get Deadline - Non-existent ID (should fail - 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create - With CLIENT token (should fail - 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "societeId": 1,
  "fiscalYear": 2024,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "documentCategory": "FACTURE_ACHAT"
}

### Delete - With CLIENT token (should fail - 403)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deadlines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Any Endpoint - Without token (should fail - 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deadlines
